Developer Terms of Use
des:
CU Voice Assistant enables you to access your credit union information and accounts in a secure touchless interaction. You can check balances and transfer funds between any of the accounts you enable at your credit union. Ask CU Voicefor your credit union's routing number, phone number, address and more. Just ask "Alexa, open CU Voice" to get started. Ask CU Voice "what can you do" to get a list of available topics and actions.
Note: that some financial information such as balances will be read aloud.
